<paragraph pageId="7" pageNumber="48">
Australia, Western Australia, Peak Charles, 10 Jan. 1982, parasitic on 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Leguminosae" genus="Oxylobium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Fabales" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" phylum="Magnoliophyta" rank="genus">
